PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of DENNIS WOOD, of Magog, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Export Development Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Marcel Dufour, whose term has expired.
